{"tid":1740884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月24日係超合作投票日","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:47:01.000Z","uid":151816,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7f2821492f006b0c2caf9937d71c7eeebd50ee","tid":1740884,"uid":151816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"各位手足可唔可以聽日後就停一停活動？ 可唔可以喺日程表加返呢個活動？<br />\n我地唔係向政府妥協 唔係聽張建宗 聶德權講 而係想踢走晒啲建制派<br />\n<br />\n小不忍則亂大謀 經歷接近半年抗爭 明白各位手足好嬲 想繼續向政府施壓 繼續黎明行動 但係政府一有藉口 就話延期 再有藉口 就話唔選 保留現有議席 政府同班建制真係訓着都笑醒 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 我地係咪應該把握呢個機會光復區議會 立法會？ <br />\n兄弟爬山 可唔可以比個機會和理非做啲野 都有好多手足參選 不如我地送晒佢地入去好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果認同 希望聽日之後各位手足忍一忍 選完再搞黎明行動亦得 手足往後喺立法會幫我地 我地繼續搞不同活動 雙贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43c0360fb9b693d511deba2c4c82fbb06e3b91d","tid":1740884,"uid":65353,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"黎明行動不能停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4S9LP9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4S9LP9.png&h=89dad0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20e63c7256bf15d2c60608d72895693efb80f1ae","tid":1740884,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a11795abd12d2d2241b5538eaa6bf6b9c59bc1b","tid":1740884,"uid":151816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"721 805 811 831 1108"},{"pid":"952c35a40955a8a71652135c6e28efd074e7e2a1","tid":1740884,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"我想投票！"},{"pid":"829109166a3a76987ec2711a97e1bab24ce79df1","tid":1740884,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-